OL,6,FThe Home Office will re-open two
OL,7,Fimmigration centres, as well as
OL,8,Frecruiting up to 100 new intelligence
OL,9,Fofficers to target people smuggling
OL,10,Fgangs. ITV political correspondent
OL,11,FShehab Khan reports
OL,13,FThe home secretary has announced new
OL,14,Fmeasures to curb illegal immigration,
OL,15,Fboost border security and increase
OL,16,Fdeportations.
