OL,3,CGovernment announces measures to
OL,4,Ctackle small boat crossings
OL,6,FYvette Cooper is aiming for the
OL,7,Fhighest removal rates since Theresa
OL,8,FMay's tenure as home secretary,
OL,9,Finsisting the home office is taking
OL,10,F"strong and clear steps to... ensure
OL,11,Fthe rules are respected and enforced".
OL,13,FThe measures include hiring up to 100
OL,14,Fspecialist intelligence and
OL,15,Finvestigations officers at the
OL,16,FNational Crime Agency (NCA) to
OL,17,Fdismantle criminal smuggling gangs and
OL,18,Fprevent dangerous boat crossings.
